{
  "stem": "19111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All we knew is that they may have been rounded up and sent to do work or help the German army carry their ammunitions.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were-- just surmised different things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But nobody could believe that they were taken to Ponar and actually shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- we discovered later on that they were shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would bring them into a holding place in Ponar there, there was a big fence, a big area they dug out big pits.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put boards along the edges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would march-- they would bring the people into a holding-- stage area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they would march 10 people at a time onto the boards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And must tell you that the Lithuanian population, the Lithuanians, were the most brutal ones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were the most cooperative with the-- with the-- with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they participated in the slaughter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were extremely brutal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And 10 people at a time were shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- there was this-- the-- the Germans followed the dictates of the final solution.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The final solution in [NON-ENGLISH] was-- was declared that all Jews have to be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the methods and the-- and the-- and the-- the time slot allowed was up to the individual heads of the Gestapo and the Nazis in the area.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Then there came a time after they have had this-- I think that before they announced the formation of the ghetto, probably around 5,000 or 6,000 Jewish men were rounded up at different actions like this here, and slaughtered in Ponar.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
